  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "- Tr\xE2u G\xE1c B\u1EBFp is a preserved buffalo meat specialty from the
    mountainous regions of Northern Vietnam, especially among ethnic minority communities.\n\n-
    The meat is stored above the kitchen fireplace for long periods.\n\n- It was
    traditionally made to preserve food during colder seasons and long trips.\n\n-
    Common seasonings include m\u1EAFc kh\xE9n, chili, ginger, and forest herbs."
