  m_text: "- B\xE1nh m\xEC is a popular Vietnamese street food made with a baguette
    filled with meats, vegetables, and sauces.\n\n- It is commonly eaten as a quick
    and filling meal because it is easy to carry around.\n\n- The dish was influenced
    by French colonial history and later adapted with Vietnamese ingredients.\n\n-
    Common ingredients include pickled carrots, cucumber, cilantro, chili, and different
    types of pork or chicken."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
