  m_text: "- C\u01A1m Ch\xE1y M\u1EAFm Ru\u1ED1c Th\u1ECBt Kho is a rice dish served
    with fermented shrimp sauce and braised pork.\n\n- The rice is prepared separately
    before being combined with the toppings and sauce.\n\n- It is considered a filling
    comfort food in some regions of Vietnam.\n\n- Main ingredients include rice,
    m\u1EAFm ru\u1ED1c, pork belly, garlic, and chili."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
